          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article07\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Width\" name=\"contentWidth\" min=\"6\" max=\"12\" value=\"8\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"range\" title=\"Paragraphs Amount\" name=\"articlesAmount\" min=\"1\" max=\"10\" value=\"3\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\">\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"/addons/socialm5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#fff8ef\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.3\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{\n            'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen}\">\n        <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{contentWidth}}\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12\">\n                            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            </p><h2>Legal Considerations for Houston Guardianship</h2><p>If your elderly or incapacitated loved one is no longer able to safely live on their own, manage their affairs, or make their own decisions, it may be time to consider petitioning for their guardianship. Houston guardianship is a serious legal role, and you should only assume it with the help of experienced guardianship attorneys near me.\n<br>\n<br>The process of becoming a legal guardian in Texas can be complicated and lengthy. The first step is to file a Petition with the probate court in the county where your proposed ward lives or resides. The petition must be accompanied by documentation from a physician attesting to the ward’s physical and mental health and incapacity.\n<br>\n<br>At this point, the court will schedule a hearing. Both you, the ward (unless medically frail or otherwise unable to attend), and your attorney will be required to testify during this hearing. The court will review all the evidence and decide if guardianship is the proper course of action. If a judge approves the petition, he or she will then name you as a legal guardian.\n<br>\n<br>You will then be responsible for filing annual reports with the court detailing how you have managed your ward’s estate and well-being. You will also be required to cooperate with investigators and examiners appointed by the court to ensure that you are adhering to all legal requirements. Failure to do so could lead to both civil and criminal complications.\n<br>\n<br>A good Houston guardianship attorney can guide you through every step of this process and help you meet all of the state’s legal obligations. They can advise you on whether a guardianship is the best course of action and can recommend alternatives like supported decision-making arrangements that will allow your loved one to retain some level of autonomy while still receiving assistance.\n<br>\n<br>While the role of a guardian can be rewarding, it is also a highly responsible position that requires an excellent grasp of the law and a sincere desire to help your ward. If you are interested in taking on this responsibility, contact an experienced Houston guardianship lawyer to discuss your options.\n<br>\n<br>The attorneys have earned the trust of clients across the Houston area and throughout Texas, including minors and adults who are not mentally capable of handling their own affairs. They understand that stepping into this role for a loved one can be overwhelming and oftentimes emotionally draining. They are committed to providing the kind of high-quality, skilled legal services necessary to protect their client’s interests.\n<br>\n<br>If you would like to talk with a Houston guardianship attorney about the legal options available to your loved one, contact a trusted legal firm today to set up a free case consultation. They can also answer any questions you have regarding the Houston guardianship hearing process in general. You may also fill out the online form on their website.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                         \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
